name: Achilles
description: Achilles was one of the demigods and the son of Thetis, a minor sea-goddess and Peleus, the king of Myrmidons

name: Aeacus
description: Aeacus was one of the demigods and the son of a son of Zeus and Aegina who was the daughter of a river god.  He was the father of Telamon and Peleus and grandfather of Ajax and Achilles

name: Aeneas
description: Aeneas was one of the demigods and the son of the goddess Aphrodite and Prince Anchises

name: Amphion
description: Amphion was one of the demigods and a son of Zeus and Antiope

name: Arcas
description: Arcas was one of the demigods and a son of Zeus and Callisto a nymph and minor goddess associated with Aphrodite

name: Clymene
description: Clymene was one of the demigods and the daughter of the Titan gods Oceanus and Tethys

name: Dardanus
description: Dardanus was a demigod and a son of Zeus and Electra who was the daughter of Atlas

name: Epaphus
description: Epaphus was one of the demigods and a son of  Zeus and Io, a priestess of the goddess Hera

name: Harmonia
description: Harmonia was one of the demigods and a daughter of Zeus and Electra

name: Helen
description: of TroyHelen of Troy was one of the demigods and a daughter of Zeus and Leda who was queen of Sparta

name: Hercules
description: Hercules (Heracles in Greek) was a demigod and a son of Zeus (Roman equivalent Jupiter) and the mortal Alcmene

name: Iasus
description: Iasus was a demigod and a son of Zeus and Electra (one of the seven daughters of Atlas and Pleione). He was the brother of Dardanus

name: Memnon
description: Memnon was one of the demigods and the son of Tithonus and Eos, aka Aurora, who was a Titan goddess of the dawn

name: Orion
description: Orion was one of the demigods and a son of the sea god Poseidon and Euryale

name: Orpheus
description: Orpheus was one of the demigods and a son of Calliope and the god Apollo

name: Perseus
description: Perseus was one of the demigods and a son of Zeus and Danae

name: Pollux
description: Pollux was one of the demigods and a son of Zeus and the mortal Leda. He was the twin brother of Castor

name: Theseus
description: Theseus was one of the demigods and a son of Poseidon and Aethra

name: Tityos
description: Tityos was one of the demigods and a son of Zeus and Elara

name: Zethes
description: Zethes was one of the demigods and a son of Boreas (the Greek god of the cold north wind and the bringer of winter) and Oreithyia, daughter of King Erechtheus of Athens. His brother was Calais
